drivers.name: brlaser
drivers.comments:
This driver is available in the Ghostscript Printer Application

Free software printer driver for Brother DCP laser printers which require the print data in a proprietary format. It is known to work with the DCP-7030 and DCP-7065DN. If you have a Brother printer which does not work with any of the other free software printer drivers, try this driver and report your results.

notes:
This printer uses a proprietary format for the job data and
      therefore the only free software driver for it is the
      "brlaser" driver.
